snippet.title: Are CHIHUAHUAS the FUNNIEST DOGS? - Funny CHIHUAHUA DOG videos that will make you LAUGH LIKE HELL
snippet.description:
This is one of our best dog compilations! Chihuahuas are sooo funny! The hardest TRY NOT TO LAUGH challenge in the World! Just look how all these chihuahuas behave, play, fail, make funny sounds, react to different things,... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
